{"tid":1361884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拉一派打一派] 唔好燒村折祠堂，拉攏鄉議局搞何君堯同白衫佬","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:12:22.000Z","uid":36775,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f184948443aef7e269188ea4968d70ba587eceb6","tid":1361884,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"共產黨點解咁成功，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為識拉一派、打一派，搞分化。</span></span></strong><br />\n本身鄉議局內部鬼打鬼，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">燒祠堂等於比機會佢地團結</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n何妖實際上係共產黨插手新界勢力嘅一粒棋<br />\n前幾年新界王劉皇發支持嘅自由黨周永勤<br />\n因為中聯辦介入而被迫退選<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/41788/%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-3%E5%80%8B%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%88%91%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%9F%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%2F41788%2F%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%258B%25A4%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2599-3%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0EuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=4b1698ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/41788/%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-3%E5%80%8B%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%88%91%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%9F%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B</a><br />\n劉皇發係新界理應係大曬，黑白甚而泛民都要忌佢三分<br />\n佢比人郁證明鄉議局嘅傳統勢力開始比中共搞，勢力開始減弱<br />\n牛屎佬一向認錢唔認人，傳統派(也都係主流派)一定對何妖有介心同想郁佢好耐<br />\n<br />\n鄉議局作為一個利益作團，而何妖作為中共代理人，插手新界事務直接影響牛屎佬自身利益，本身都好多仇家。家陣何妖同白衫搞到咁大獲同將鄉黑呢個問題放上水面，影響好多牛屎佬利益，例如元朗樓價跌、無人流，內部一定對佢同白衫好不滿。加上何妖之前連劉皇發都夠膽郁，拉攏鄉議局可以比個機會劉業強幫佢老豆復仇(睇佢笑得幾撚真心就知)，鏟起班人，黑食黑。同時也都比個機會鄉議局洗底，做形象工程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係721睇直播時都的確好撚嬲，也好想燒咗牛屎佬祠堂<br />\n但係冷靜之後，想勸大家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千其唔好燒祠堂</span></span></strong><br />\n點解<br />\n1. 牛屎地有多外姓人，易誤傷副車。<br />\n2.燒祠堂係直接同成個新界牛屎佬宣戰，班牛屎佬好重傳統，咁做係迫鄉議局歸邊。<br />\n3.風險太大，好容易損失義士。<br />\n4.比真心去保家衛國嘅牛屎佬知佢地比何妖擺上枱，何妖自然有人搵佢算帳。<br />\n5.唔洗自己出手，等鄉議局內部自己黑食黑。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>希望大家唔好比怒氣影響而去燒祠堂，反而唔燒祠堂和搞到佢地鬼打鬼先達到最大效益同成果。</strong>"},{"pid":"00c5924f4dbf7c4bb77e4f57f5982d13ac3e0c3b","tid":1361884,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a949ea74fa4ad15507f36bb2f83c72304ec08e74","tid":1361884,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4dd8a6cf2bb433b52db9fc9cb938b284dbec3861","tid":1361884,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:15:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c066f43f2f36c8dd665b0a6e889a049c05d54730","tid":1361884,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:17:07.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n[置頂] 打完飛機未，打完就入黎傾正經野呀！！ 727 反黑遊行 5+1 訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpKaqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpKaqS</a>"},{"pid":"3ca784be94c79694d477e0138d603cef566feec8","tid":1361884,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4DG9Hr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4DG9Hr.png&h=32ade980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n727 發動全港紀律部隊保護市民遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360600</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa9b5b00356c05a169020457938a0896e3fcede8","tid":1361884,"uid":272010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ed824e1876a62b14d755d9b7925bc7b174bbe7","tid":1361884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:12:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727對準鄉黑：南邊圍福德堂</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i1.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg?fit=1280%2C852&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FIMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg%3Ffit%3D1280%252C852%26ssl%3D1&h=144559cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180303/photo/bkn-20180303174105327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180303182522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180303174105327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180303182522&h=b7b43767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.postimg.cc/d1RbdsTg/yl-1-2-gate.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fd1RbdsTg%2Fyl-1-2-gate.jpg&h=53120000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當日疑接載白衫鄉黑的車牌：<br />\n<br />\nVW 9089<br />\nWZ 7266<br />\nNT 21<br />\nVL 9886<br />\nTM 790"}]}